{"id":"c6f8a7a6-758e-4c16-9cb5-821017b2474d","name":"Soshiro Hoshina","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">. . . <em>So don’t let go</em>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꒰͡&nbsp;&nbsp; ִ&nbsp; <strong>un-established relationship</strong> ׂ &nbsp; &nbsp; ͡꒱</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_efcb663b-e791-44e5-a07e-5058dee90776.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">FEMPOV, SFW &amp; LONG INTRO</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_d628474e-f6a4-407b-ba6e-13f13e5421d5.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>Soshiro pushes through the heavy metal door of the abandoned shelter, his eyes half-open, searching for any signs of danger. He takes in the emptiness around him, then glances back over his shoulder to make sure you’re still following him.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>He hadn’t thought his evening would end up like this—ducking into a lifeless shelter with his ex-girlfriend. Several Kaiju had struck the city, and both his squad and yours had been deployed to handle the threat. He hadn’t seen you since the break up. But as things went south and lines broke, you’d been cut off from your squads, having no choice but to take refuge here.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>He’s not sure what to say. Maybe a part of him still resents how things ended.</em></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_87da9f74-adbf-4de5-ada6-5906672a4e92.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ɪ <strong>ᴅᴏɴ’ᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏɴᴛʀᴏʟ ʜᴏᴡ ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴏᴛ ᴀɴsᴡᴇʀs. ʀᴇᴘᴇᴛɪᴛɪᴠᴇ ᴡᴏʀᴅs, ᴏᴏᴄ, sᴘᴇᴀᴋɪɴɢ ғᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜ—ɪᴛ’s ᴛʜᴇ ʟʟᴍ, ᴏᴘᴇɴᴀɪ ᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴊᴀɪʟʙʀᴇᴀᴋ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴅᴏ <strong>ɴᴏᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏᴘʏ, ʀᴇᴘᴏsᴛ ᴏʀ sᴛᴇᴀʟ. ʀᴇᴠɪᴇᴡs ᴀʀᴇ ᴀᴘᴘʀᴇᴄɪᴀᴛᴇᴅ.</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_6bccd304-ca97-4238-90d2-610cbcf2db98.webp?width=1000\"></p><p></p><h5 style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsYCF_3PFwUJmTsven90r0lmpaoUq7oCT62wfpsLbLmGFkMQ/closedform\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">suggestion form</mark></span></a><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsYCF_3PFwUJmTsven90r0lmpaoUq7oCT62wfpsLbLmGFkMQ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\"> </mark></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">✦ art credits: ?</span></h5><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h5 style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1015XS2pXH23wOfqYe_nTQ_5GdOfqN-XItrXqSYUpOx8\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">bot masterlist</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"> ✦ </span><a href=\"https://discord.gg/KBJb97nKT6\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">discord server</span></a></h5><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_87b83093-efd8-434f-bd70-fc4543e385b4.webp","creator":"itafushigf","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","💔 Angst","👩 FemPov","🌗 Switch"],"chats":3363,"messages":38450,"c